column10: PIN3 intron of A. thaliana MEGABLAST against plants (taxid 3193)
MEGABLAST hits are very well-aligned sequences
Hence, the output of MEGABLAST are short sequences
I took the accession number of the MEGABLAST results and BLAST PIN3 intron against it (BLASTN; loose alignments allowed)
This allows the full sequence related to PIN3 to be located
